### 1. Get all active sessions (Cashier view)

GET http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/sessions

###

### 2. Get full bill details for a specific session

GET http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/sessions/1

###

### 3. Mark session as COMPLETED (after customer pays)

PUT http://localhost:5000/api/cashier/sessions/1/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "payment_method": "cash"
}

